## 2026-04-05 - Unify the three undo/redo systems into a single timeline
- Merged local undo, server operation log, and git commits/snapshots into a single chronological "Activity" timeline in `HistoryPanel.tsx`. The separate "This session" collapsible section was removed; local undo entries are now inline in the timeline sorted by synthetic timestamps (Date.now() - index * 100ms, most recent first).
